result:
<a-modal
  :title="title"
  :width="800"
  :visible="visible"
  :confirmLoading="confirmLoading"
  @ok="handleOk"
  @cancel="handleCancel"
  cancelText="关闭">
  
  <a-spin :spinning="confirmLoading">
    <a-form :form="form">
    
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="支付金额">
        <a-input-number class="rechange-num" v-decorator="[ 'money', validatorRules.money ]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="实际获取独家币">
        <a-input-number class="rechange-num" v-decorator="[ 'trueMoney', validatorRules.trueMoney ]" />
      </a-form-item>

    </a-form>
  </a-spin>
</a-modal>
